 Library tab houses the photo organizer. Under this tab, you can organize photos by keyword, date or category. You also can assign star ratings to each of your photos and later sort by ratings.  When you import your photos, the software automatically checks for duplicate photos and alerts you if any are found, saving you from manually removing these images. The program also has a backup manager to help protect your photos.","When creating albums to organize your photo, you can create a Smart Album, which automatically groups your images together based on criteria you set. In other words, you can create an album with photos that share the same date, location, holiday or keyword, and then any photos you add to your collection later on are automatically added to those albums if they match the criteria.","In addition to the full-featured photo organizer, the software has a selection of editing tools you can find under the Develop tab. You can apply basic edits like rotating or cropping your photos or add stunning effects to your images. With 47 creative filters, you can transform the colors and textures in your photos.","The software also has a batch editor. With this feature, you can add the same effect to multiple photos. It serves as a timesaver when uploading and editing hundreds of photos. The program has useful correction tools. For example, there is a straighten tool, which corrects crooked photos so they appear straight. It also has red eye removal and touch-up tools to remedy any blemishes found in your photos.","In addition to the organizer and editor, this photo organizing software has several sharing options. You can post your photos directly to sites like Facebook, Flickr and Dropbox. This feature makes it easy to show your photos to your friends. You also can create slideshows or send an email of your photos directly from the program. While you cannot post directly to online photo galleries, you can print off your photos using the program’s templates and share hard copies of them.","PhotoStack offers quality support with its product. With a knowledge base full of resources, you can access tutorials, FAQs and a user forum. If you have direct questions for technical support, you can contact representatives by phone and email."]},"id":"a94032e4-3bc5-4492-a601-ec967334daf9","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"a2213ff4-abfb-4bba-a43a-e1914f5aa537","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Between the program’s advanced capabilities and assortment of tools, you can organize, edit and share your photos using Serif PhotoStack. The software’s clean interface makes it easy to quickly access the tools you need to manage a large collection of photos. If you are looking for a photo organizer software that offers editing tools and sharing options, PhotoStack is a good option."]},"id":"3e9d2db2-36d5-409e-90c5-322ce479f423","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_66772","url":"/serif-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"rebecca-spear","url":"/author/rebecca-spear","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Rebecca Spear","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"X8Ccy4LP9pMXtXdurbSshX","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2015-09-03T16:35:46Z","datePublished":"2015-09-03T16:35:46Z","name":"Serif PhotoStack","synopsis":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current Photo Organizing Software Reviews here.","review":{"rating":87,"verdict":"When you use Serif PhotoStack, you can organize, edit and share your photos all in one easy-to-use application.","pros":["When you create a Smart Album, the software automatically groups images together in terms of the criteria you set."],"cons":["While this program shares photos to social media sites, you cannot post your images to online photo galleries directly fr